result.name: Nam Kee Noodle

reviews.text:
One of the best Mara湯 base noodles! If you are a beef lover, please try Woo-Ma-Wang(牛魔王)!! So yummmmmyyyy!! 
Also you can choose the toppings and the level of spicy. Very good and reasonable price so you can eat everyday hahaha 
It comes out very quick and it's a franchise so if you google it, you can find many places. 
Enjoy☆
Famous chain noodle restaurant in HK. Tasty and fairly priced.

Good cheap eat! What can you moan about!!
I love the spicy pork slices and sour and spicy soup based noodles!!

Nourshing and comforting bowl of noodle soup. Sour veggies make the flavor have a nice blend. You can add in extra spices or vinegar if you like. 

Tip: Napkins are available but you'll need to find the statiost with a napkain holder near the extra bowls.
Great bowl of noodles with pork and shrimp dumplings in fish skin wrapping. Pickled sour veggies with it are great too. Goes well with a side of milk tea!

reviews.text: 通常吃下午茶,位於尖沙咀區,價錢算不貴,現大多粉麵店或餐廳，一碗粉麵都超HK$30.-, 南記下午茶20蚊都有交易（春卷/魚片/魚腐/魚餃/冬菰......尚有其它選擇...双并+生菜+豆漿, 要飽肚D...選26蚊的招牌粉麵啦（牛丸/魚片/春卷各件+粉/麵+豆漿/汽水）😋
